Titolo: Ford Mustang: The Legend Lives

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Ford Mustang: The Legend Lives is a racing video game developed by Eutechnyx and published by 2K Games for the PlayStation 2 (PS2) and Xbox. It is part of the Ford Racing series, following Ford Racing 3. The game was released in the United States on April 19, 2005, and received mixed reviews. This is the first Ford Racing game to not be released on PC.